      "heading": "These Regulations may be cited as the National Pension Title",
      "text": "Scheme (Pensionable Earnings)(Amendment) Regulations, 2021,\nand shall be read as one with the National Pension Scheme S.I. No. 22\n(Pensionable Earnings) Regulations, 2000, in these Regulations of 2000\nreferred to as the principal Regulations."
